---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Menapia is an operational atmospheric profiling company building drone-based observing networks for forecasting, climate research, and decision systems."
>
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 sm:pt-40 sm:pb-28">
    <div class="container-wide section-padding">
      <SectionHeading
        tag="About"
        title="Building the atmospheric observing infrastructure the world needs"
        subtitle="Menapia is an operational atmospheric profiling company. We design, build, and operate vertically profiling drone networks that deliver calibrated atmospheric observations to forecast centres, research programmes, and decision-makers."
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="py-20 border-t border-slate-800/50">
    <div class="container-wide section-padding">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Our mission</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            The lower atmosphere — the boundary layer where weather begins, where pollutants concentrate,
            and where renewable energy is generated — remains critically under-observed. Radiosondes
            are sparse and expensive. Ground-based remote sensing has limitations. Satellite retrievals
            lack vertical resolution near the surface.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            We are building a new class of observing infrastructure: networks of vertically profiling
            drones that collect calibrated atmospheric columns routinely, affordably, and at the
            spatial density that modern forecasting demands.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Our values</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <div class="shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-atmos-500 mt-2"></div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-white font-medium">Measurement integrity</p>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-1">We do not compromise on calibration, traceability, or quality control. Our observations must be trustworthy.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <div class="shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-atmos-500 mt-2"></div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-white font-medium">Operational discipline</p>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-1">Reliable observations require reliable operations. We design for sustained, routine deployment — not one-off demonstrations.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <div class="shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-atmos-500 mt-2"></div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-white font-medium">Open collaboration</p>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-1">We work within the research and forecasting community, not apart from it. Collaboration amplifies impact.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <div class="shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-atmos-500 mt-2"></div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-white font-medium">Standards alignment</p>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-1">We deliver data in the formats and standards that the meteorological community expects and depends on.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Operational discipline -->
  <section class="py-20 border-t border-slate-800/50">
    <div class="container-wide section-padding">
      <SectionHeading
        tag="Operations"
        title="Operational discipline"
        subtitle="We approach atmospheric observation as an operational challenge, not just an engineering one."
      />

      <div class="mt-10 glass rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Collecting a single vertical profile is straightforward. Collecting thousands of profiles,
          consistently, across sites, in all weather, with full quality control and timely
          delivery — that is the challenge we have built our company around.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Our operational processes cover flight scheduling, sensor calibration, data processing,
          quality control, format encoding, and delivery — all designed to run routinely and
          at scale.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Careers -->
  <section class="py-20 border-t border-slate-800/50">
    <div class="container-narrow section-padding text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white">Join us</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-400 max-w-lg mx-auto">
        We are a small team solving a hard problem. If you are interested in atmospheric science,
        drone operations, data engineering, or building observing networks — we would like to hear from you.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/menapia-site/contact/"
        class="mt-6 inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-atmos-600 hover:bg-atmos-500 text-white font-medium rounded-xl transition-colors text-sm"
      >
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
